OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start to Friday but
OL,6,Fturning cloudier into the afternoon
OL,7,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain pushing
OL,8,Fnorthwards. Showers becoming heavy,
OL,9,Fpossibly thundery by the evening.
OL,10,FFeeling warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers clearing northwards
OL,13,Fthis evening with cloud lingering over
OL,14,Fthe hills overnight bringing some
OL,15,Fdrizzle in places. Another mild night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
