OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fdrizzle over the hills, however the
OL,7,Fcloud will break allowing some sunnier
OL,8,Fintervals to develop. Rain arriving
OL,9,Flater in the evening, locally heavy at
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FShowers
OL,13,For longer spells of rain likely
OL,14,Fthrough Sunday and into Monday,
OL,15,Fpossibly thundery. A few showers still
OL,16,Fpossible Tuesday. Feeling cooler early
OL,17,Fnext week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
